"548","<TEXT>"
"549","77L New accounting pronouncement"
"550","In January 2013, ASU 2013 01, Clarifying the Scope of"
"551","Disclosures about Offsetting Assets and Liabilities, amended"
"552","ASU No. 2011 11, Disclosures about Offsetting Assets and"
"553","Liabilities. The ASUs create new disclosure requirements"
"554","requiring entities to disclose both gross and net information"
"555","for derivatives and other financial instruments that are either"
"556","offset in the Statement of assets and liabilities or subject to"
"557","an enforceable master netting arrangement or similar agreement."
"558","The disclosure requirements are effective for annual reporting"
"559","periods beginning on or after January 1, 2013 and interim"
"560","periods within those annual periods. Putnam Management is"
"561","currently evaluating the application of ASUs 2013 01 and 2011 11"
"562","and their impact, if any, on the funds financial statements."
