"625","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"626","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum"
"627","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"628","semi-monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"629","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"630","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"631","investments under the minimum."
